Exercise 8: Convert the following datetime into a string

Given:

given_date = datetime(2020, 2, 25)

Expected output:

"2020-02-25 00:00:00"

code:
____________________________________________________________

from datetime import datetime
given_date = datetime(2020, 2, 25)
string = str(given_date)
print(string)

